trans-unit.source: Extends design-time behavior for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"></xref> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Utvider utformingen virkemåte for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"> </xref> Web serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: Extend the CreateUserWizardDesigner class if you want to create a designer for a class that extends the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Utvide klassen CreateUserWizardDesigner Hvis du vil opprette en utformer for en klasse som utvider den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>Web serverkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> object for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> objekt for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion"></xref> object for each step associated with the underlying wizard control, and then adds it to the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion"> </xref> objekt for hvert trinn tilknyttet underliggende veiviserkontrollen, og legger det til den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> to which regions associated with the wizard control are added.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref> skal legges til som områder som er knyttet til veiviseren for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> object associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Converts the child controls associated with the underlying wizard control to a custom navigation template.
trans-unit.target: Konverterer underordnede kontroller som er knyttet til underliggende veiviserkontrollen til en egendefinert navigasjon mal.

trans-unit.source: Gets the HTML that provides information about the specified exception.
trans-unit.target: Henter HTML som inneholder informasjon om det angitte unntaket.

trans-unit.source: This method is typically called after an error has been encountered at design time.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles vanligvis etter at det oppstod en feil under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The exception that occurred.
trans-unit.target: Unntak som oppstod.

trans-unit.source: The HTML for the specified exception.
trans-unit.target: HTML for den angitte unntaket.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the designer and loads the specified component.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer designer og laster inn den angitte komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The control element being designed.
trans-unit.target: Elementet kontrollen blir utformet.

trans-unit.source: Exposes the properties associated with each default step through the property grid on the designer tool.
trans-unit.target: Viser egenskaper som er knyttet til hver standard steg egenskapen rutenettet på designer verktøyet.

trans-unit.source: The PreFilterProperties method provides a way to add items to the dictionary of properties that a designer exposes.
trans-unit.target: Metoden PreFilterProperties kan ikke legge til elementer i liste over egenskaper som en designer viser.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of properties are the names of the properties.
trans-unit.target: Nøkler i ordlisten for egenskaper er navnene på egenskapene.

trans-unit.source: The objects are of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Objektene er av typen <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor"></xref> objects that represent the properties of the component's base class.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor"> </xref> objekter som representerer egenskaper for komponentens basisklasse.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of properties are property names.
trans-unit.target: Nøkler i ordlisten for egenskaper er egenskapsnavn.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer uses the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"></xref> control itself to generate the design-time HTML or uses a temporarily created copy.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer bruker den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"> </xref> kontrollerer seg selv for å generere utformingen HTML eller bruker en midlertidig opprettet kopi.

trans-unit.source: When the value of the UsePreviewControl property is `true`, the designer uses a temporary copy of the wizard control to generate the design-time HTML; when the value of UsePreviewControl is `false`, the designer uses the wizard control itself to generate the design-time HTML.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien for egenskapen UsePreviewControl er `true`, designer bruker en midlertidig kopi kontrollens veiviseren til å generere utformingen HTML; når verdien for UsePreviewControl er `false`, designer bruker selve veiviserkontrollen til å generere utformingen HTML.

trans-unit.source: The value of UsePreviewControl modifies the return value of the designer's <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for UsePreviewControl endrer returverdien for utformeren <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: When UsePreviewControl is `true`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> returns a copy of the wizard control.
trans-unit.target: Når UsePreviewControl er `true`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>returnerer en kopi av veiviserkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: When UsePreviewControl is `false`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> returns the wizard control itself.
trans-unit.target: Når UsePreviewControl er `false`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>returnerer selve for kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the wizard control is marked with a class-level <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> attribute, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> is ignored, because the value of UsePreviewControl is always `true`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis veiviserkontrollen er merket med en klasse nivå <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>attributtet i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>ignoreres, fordi verdien for UsePreviewControl alltid `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>
